### 5. Eager Test — `OrderProcessor_FullWorkflow_Succeeds` (line 54)

Calls **7 distinct production methods** (`ValidateOrder`, `CalculateTotal`, `ApplyDiscount`, `ReserveInventory`, `ProcessPayment`, `SendConfirmation`, `UpdateOrderHistory`) but only asserts the final status. If it fails, you have no idea which step broke.

**Fix:** Either test each method independently, or if this is meant as an integration test, add intermediate assertions and rename to make the intent clear.

